Uses of Package
net.hypixel.skyblock.client.gui.screen

  • Packages that use net.hypixel.skyblock.client.gui.screen 
    Package Description
    net.hypixel.skyblock.client.gui.screen
    Holds everything related to Screen.
  • Classes in net.hypixel.skyblock.client.gui.screen used by net.hypixel.skyblock.client.gui.screen 
    Class and Description
    AbstractBackpackScreen
    Serve as a base for Backpack Screen
    AbstractMinionScreen.Button
    Serve as a base for buttons to be displayed on this screen.
    AbstractMinionScreen.EmptyButton
    When this AbstractMinionScreen.Button is pressed, automatically empty all Item from this AbstractMinionBlock.
    Also empties MinionChestBlock if the AbstractMinionBlock has one.
    AbstractMinionScreen.UpgradeButton
    When this AbstractMinionScreen.Button is pressed, automatically upgrade this AbstractMinionBlock to the next AbstractMinionTileEntity.MinionTier.
    This AbstractMinionScreen.Button will not do anything if the AbstractMinionBlock is at the maximum AbstractMinionTileEntity.MinionTier
    or if the PlayerEntity does not have the required materials.
    MinionChestScreen
    A basis for MinionChest Screen.
    TimeSaverScreen.Button
    An AbstractButton that allows the PlayerEntity to interact with TimeSaverScreen.
    TimeSaverScreen.SpriteButton
    A TimeSaverScreen.Button that allows textures to render over this.
